    <tr class="d-block">
      <td class="d-block comment-body markdown-body  js-comment-body">
          <p dir="auto">Stabilizing this would not make <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="822306359" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/82768" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/rust-lang/rust/issues/82768/hovercard" href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/82768">#82768</a> irrelevant because of people trying to provide backward compatibility.</p>
<p dir="auto">Clap's MSRV is 1.46.0. We would like to keep it the same and use the <code class="notranslate">doc</code> feature flag to conditionally enable the <code class="notranslate">doc = include_str!</code> when building docs. That way, MSRV is bumped to 1.53.0 only when building the docs.</p>

      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
