          <blockquote>
<p dir="auto">This is not specifically about proc-macros: <a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/78835#issuecomment-845831023" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/rust-lang/rust/issues/78835/hovercard">#78835 (comment)</a></p>
</blockquote>
<p dir="auto">So if I read that correctly, this is supported:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-rust notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="#[some_derive_macro = something!()]
struct X {}"><pre class="notranslate"><span class="pl-c1">#<span class="pl-kos">[</span>some_derive_macro = <span class="pl-en">something</span><span class="pl-en">!</span><span class="pl-kos">(</span><span class="pl-kos">)</span><span class="pl-kos">]</span></span>
<span class="pl-k">struct</span> <span class="pl-smi">X</span> <span class="pl-kos">{</span><span class="pl-kos">}</span></pre></div>
<p dir="auto">Bot not this:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-rust notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="#[some_derive_macro(attribute1 = something!())]
struct X {}"><pre class="notranslate"><span class="pl-c1">#<span class="pl-kos">[</span>some_derive_macro<span class="pl-kos">(</span>attribute1 = something!<span class="pl-kos">(</span><span class="pl-kos">)</span><span class="pl-kos">)</span><span class="pl-kos">]</span></span>
<span class="pl-k">struct</span> <span class="pl-smi">X</span> <span class="pl-kos">{</span><span class="pl-kos">}</span></pre></div>
<p dir="auto">Is that what <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="738270652" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/78835" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/rust-lang/rust/issues/78835/hovercard?comment_id=845831023&amp;comment_type=issue_comment" href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/78835#issuecomment-845831023">#78835 (comment)</a> is saying?</p>
<p dir="auto">Thanks.</p>

      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</task-lists>


